Q. Virtualization?
â˜… Multiple VMs run on a single physical machine.
â˜… Each vm have its own OS,CPU,RAM,Disk,Network.
â˜… Each VM is isolated â€“ one tenant cannot access anotherâ€™s data
â˜… Helps in cost reduction and efficient resource utilization
Q. Multi-Tenancy?
