Q. What is subnetting?
â” Let's consider 3 diff network - deepa,hr,azure
â” when the req come = need CIDR (10.0.0.0/24)
â—† What is this 24?
â—† this means 32-24 =8 2^8 =256 machines
â—† 10.0.0.0 to 10.0.0.255
â” for 3 diff network we need table
â” network 1 2 4 8 16 32 64 128 256
â” host 256 128 64 32 16 8 4 2 1
â” subnet mask /24 /25 /26 /27 /28 /29 /30 /31 /32
â—† 24 =256 machines
â” now i want to create a seperate network for hr (divide network to 3(hr,deepa,azure))
â” no way u can create 3 network = only option = dividing into 4
â” each network i get 64 machines
â” hr ip range = 10.0.0.1 - 10.0.0.62
â” prblm :
â—† network ip(10.0.0.0),broadcast ip(10.0.0.63)
â” 10.0.0.0/26
â” deepa = range =10.0.0.65 - 10.0.0.126
â” network =10.0.0.64 broadcast =10.0.0.127
â” 10.0.0.64/26
â” azure = range =10.0.0.129 - 10.0.0.190
â” network =10.0.0.128 broadcast =10.0.0.191
â” 10.0.0.128/26
â” Network ip: 1st ip is reserved for network
â” Broadcast ip : the last ip is reserved for broadcast
