Q. Azure IP Reservation Rule?
â” Azure reserves 5 ip (first 4 and last1)
â” First 4 IPs: Reserved for protocols and Azure services (e.g., .0 - .3)
â” Last IP: Reserved for network broadcast (e.g., .255)
