Q. what is automation account?
â” An Automation Account in Azure is a cloud service that provides a way to automate repetitive
tasks and processes in your Azure environment, such as resource management, configuration,
monitoring, and maintenance tasks.
â” It enables the automation of actions like starting or stopping virtual machines (VMs), scaling
resources, deploying updates, managing configurations, and handling system eventsâ€”without
needing to do so manually each time.
â—† Key features:
â— Runbooks: automate tasks like stopping vm
â— Update Management: update vm to make it secure
â— Scheduling: set tasks to run at specific time
